#: ../../source/news/releases/1.2.x/announcing-1.2.8/index.rst:12
msgid ""
"Fix a bug introduced by `our October 8th security release </news/security"
"/istio-security-2019-005>`_ which incorrectly calculated HTTP header and "
"body sizes (`Issue 17735 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/17735>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.2.x/announcing-1.2.8/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"Fix a minor bug where endpoints still remained in /clusters while scaling"
" a deployment to 0 replica (`Issue 14336 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/14336>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.2.x/announcing-1.2.8/index.rst:21
msgid ""
"Fix Helm upgrade process to correctly update mesh policy for mutual TLS "
"(`Issue 16170 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/16170>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.2.x/announcing-1.2.8/index.rst:24
msgid ""
"Fix inconsistencies in the destination service label for TCP connection "
"opened/closed metrics (`Issue 17234 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/17234>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.2.x/announcing-1.2.8/index.rst:28
msgid ""
"Fix the Istio secret cleanup mechanism (`Issue 17122 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/17122>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.2.x/announcing-1.2.8/index.rst:31
msgid ""
"Fix the Mixer Stackdriver adapter encoding process to handle invalid "
"UTF-8 (`Issue 16966 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/16966>`_)."
msgstr ""

